name achemso
category Package
revision 79461
shortdesc Support for American Chemical Society journal submissions
longdesc The bundle provides a BibTeX style file following the
longdesc requirements of the American Chemical Society (ACS), and a
longdesc package to pass settings to the BibTeX style. It also includes
longdesc a class which was used for submission support in the past. All
longdesc of this material is largely of historical interest and is
longdesc retained for stability. For new material, the chem-acs style is
longdesc available for bibliographies, and a short template for the ACS
longdesc website is better suited to submission.
