name bashful
category Package
revision 25597
shortdesc Invoke bash commands from within LaTeX
longdesc The package makes it possible to execute Unix bash shell
longdesc scripts from within LaTeX. The main application is in writing
longdesc computer-science texts, in which you want to make sure the
longdesc programs listed in the document are executed directly from the
longdesc input. The package may use other Unix shells than bash, but
longdesc does not work without modification in a Windows environment.
longdesc The package requires the -shell-escape flag when LaTeX is
longdesc processing your document.
