name beamer-reveal
category Package
revision 78638
shortdesc Convert beamer slides to reveal.js HTML presentations
longdesc Beamer is a very powerful and convenient document class to
longdesc create presentations and slides. However, integrating
longdesc multimedia in it, is still a bit of a faff. The (limited)
longdesc functionality heavily relies on the availability of acroread.
longdesc This package allows you to convert your beamer presentation to
longdesc the reveal.js framework, rendering your presentation as an HTML
longdesc website in your browser. This allows for easy incorporation of
longdesc videos, audio fragments, iframe chunks, images and LaTeX
longdesc animations.
