name binarytree
category Package
revision 41777
shortdesc Drawing binary trees using TikZ
longdesc This package provides an easy but flexible way to draw binary
longdesc trees using TikZ. A path specification and the setting of
longdesc various options determine the style for each edge of the tree.
longdesc There is support for the external library of TikZ which does
longdesc not affect externalization of the rest of the TikZ figures in
longdesc the document. There is an option to use automatic file naming:
longdesc useful if the trees are often moved around.
