longdesc recent version (3.0+) of PGF and TikZ for the drawing, hence,
longdesc it is mainly a set of TikZ styles that makes the drawing of
longdesc bond graphs easier. Compared to the bondgraph package this
longdesc package relies more on TikZ styles and less on macros, to
longdesc generate the drawings. As such it can be more flexible than
longdesc his, but requires more TikZ knowledge of the user.
